msg.text: This device does not have a pininfo table.
There is no FNC column in the pininfo table.
Unable to locate PCS comp '$$s' at site '$$s' due to unbonded APIOs for $$s package.\n
$$d PCS comps in netlist while only $$d sites are available.\n
Signal "$$s" (driven by PCS comp "$$s") cannot drive DCS input.
PCS '$$s' cannot be locked at site '$$s' due to unbonded APIOs in package '$$s'.\n
Unable to recognize location of pcs site $$s\n.
Unable to place PCS comp '$$s'; no legal site available.\n
Invalid NC_NODE '$$s' connecting PCS and APIO site '$$s'.\n

PCS comp "$$s" at site "$$s": QCLK signal "$$s" drives this PCS's "$$s" input. Therefore, this signal must be routed from quadrant "$$s" according to hardware connectivity; however, this is inconsistent with the QCLK preference of this signal (quadrant$$s $$s) and will cause routing failure.
